blog.name: musaschemicalromance
blog.title: Winx Club must be queer-positive.
blog.description: Winx Club is a show of firsts - the first show to feature persons of color in major roles, and one of the first to give relatively gender non-conforming characters prominent roles too. Such a show can, and has served to be inspirational for many children who believe they do not conform to ascribed societal norms in relation to their gender and race. Any efforts against celebrating differences will continue to cause individuals to feel alientated in all other spheres of life for a long time. A TV show like Winx Club should attempt to set an example for embracing difference, not repressing or shaming it.
